00:59:03,857 --> 00:59:05,292
Are you okay?

556
00:59:07,727 --> 00:59:08,994
It was my fault.

557
00:59:08,995 --> 00:59:11,020
What was?

558
00:59:11,131 --> 00:59:13,599
Bobby went to jail
because of me.

559
00:59:13,600 --> 00:59:17,036
What do you mean?

560
00:59:19,573 --> 00:59:23,203
We were at that bar
on Rivington.

561
00:59:23,510 --> 00:59:26,879
Some guy followed me
into the bathroom.

562
00:59:26,880 --> 00:59:29,181
He pushed me
up against the wall...,

563
00:59:29,182 --> 00:59:31,884
...and put his hand over my mouth.

564
00:59:31,885 --> 00:59:34,046
What?

565
00:59:36,089 --> 00:59:41,152
Next thing I know, Bobby...,

566
00:59:41,261 --> 00:59:47,261
...he hit him so hard that I heard
the bones in his face crack.

567
00:59:47,734 --> 00:59:50,999
And he didn't stop.

568
00:59:51,104 --> 00:59:54,073
The more I cried,
the more Bobby hit him.

569
00:59:54,074 --> 00:59:56,414
Al, he killed someone.

570
00:59:58,878 --> 01:00:01,380
I don't know what to do.

571
01:00:01,381 --> 01:00:02,881
I mean, he did all that time.

572
01:00:02,882 --> 01:00:05,517
Maybe he'll hurt you some day.

573
01:00:05,518 --> 01:00:06,819
It's...it's not him.

574
01:00:06,820 --> 01:00:09,914
It never was.

575
01:00:10,023 --> 01:00:13,049
He was only trying to help.

576
01:00:15,095 --> 01:00:19,429
I just want you
to be careful, okay?

577
01:00:19,532 --> 01:00:20,556
Yeah.

578
01:01:16,890 --> 01:01:20,615
What the hell's your problem,
man?

579
01:01:37,143 --> 01:01:39,198
You all right, bro?

580
01:01:39,813 --> 01:01:44,250
Uh, I got blood coming out
of my ears.

581
01:01:44,350 --> 01:01:46,785
How the hell did you
do that, man?

582
01:01:46,786 --> 01:01:47,886
I don't know.

583
01:01:47,887 --> 01:01:49,488
Go see a doctor.

584
01:01:49,489 --> 01:01:50,823
I got to finish my shift, man.

585
01:01:50,824 --> 01:01:51,924
Go see a doctor.

586
01:01:51,925 --> 01:01:53,592
Blood coming out of your ears
ain't normal.

587
01:01:53,593 --> 01:01:54,693
Are you sick or something?

588
01:01:54,694 --> 01:01:59,256
You doing okay?

589
01:01:59,365 --> 01:02:01,492
How do you mean?

590
01:02:01,601 --> 01:02:04,069
I'm not gonna pretend like
I know you...,

591
01:02:04,070 --> 01:02:09,174
...but you been falling apart
since you took this job.

592
01:02:09,175 --> 01:02:15,175
Um, if I try to explain it,
it's not gonna sound right.

593
01:02:15,548 --> 01:02:18,517
When I came out of recovery,
I started over too.

594
01:02:18,518 --> 01:02:20,552
I had a sponsor to talk to
when things got out of hand.

595
01:02:20,553 --> 01:02:22,054
You know what I'm saying?

596
01:02:22,055 --> 01:02:26,125
You need someone to talk to,
or you're gonna fall apart.

597
01:02:26,126 --> 01:02:27,126
Go home.

598
01:02:27,227 --> 01:02:30,321
I'll lock up.

599
01:02:30,430 --> 01:02:35,231
All right.

600
01:02:39,305 --> 01:02:40,439
I'm leaving the city.

601
01:02:40,440 --> 01:02:41,540
I can't stay here.

602
01:02:41,541 --> 01:02:42,541
Why?

603
01:02:42,642 --> 01:02:44,009
I think whatever's...

604
01:02:44,010 --> 01:02:45,944
...whatever happened to my mother
is happening to me.

605
01:02:45,945 --> 01:02:48,614
And I...I just...
I just got to make it stop.

606
01:02:48,615 --> 01:02:49,707
What?

607
01:02:49,816 --> 01:02:52,979
What?

608
01:02:53,086 --> 01:02:56,455
I'm hear...I'm hearing sounds...,

609
01:02:56,456 --> 01:03:01,136
...and I am seeing people
who aren't there.

610
01:03:01,961 --> 01:03:05,488
Bobby,
your mother was sick.

611
01:03:05,598 --> 01:03:07,998
She wasn't crazy.

612
01:03:08,101 --> 01:03:10,702
Something made her crazy.

613
01:03:10,703 --> 01:03:13,001
Maybe you leaving...

614
01:03:13,106 --> 01:03:16,564
...did make her depressed.

615
01:03:19,412 --> 01:03:21,013
You deserted her...,

616
01:03:21,014 --> 01:03:26,611
...like you deserted a lot
of people in your life.

617
01:03:38,865 --> 01:03:40,490
You got tables.

618
01:03:44,771 --> 01:03:46,534
I got to go.

619
01:05:30,000 --> 01:05:31,530
Open the door!

620
01:05:34,580 --> 01:05:35,948
Open the door, please!

621
01:05:35,949 --> 01:05:38,484
I know you're in there!

622
01:07:18,751 --> 01:07:20,352
What do you want?

623
01:07:20,353 --> 01:07:23,618
What do you want?

624
01:07:24,824 --> 01:07:27,829
- Good morning, sir.
- Yeah.

625
01:07:28,561 --> 01:07:30,028
Do you know a Joseph Wright?

626
01:07:30,029 --> 01:07:31,930
He lives down the hall from you.

627
01:07:31,931 --> 01:07:33,098
I just moved in.

628
01:07:33,099 --> 01:07:34,766
Heard anything
out of the ordinary?

629
01:07:34,767 --> 01:07:36,701
Seen anyone suspicious?

630
01:07:36,702 --> 01:07:39,637
No.

631
01:07:39,739 --> 01:07:41,873
The neighbors told us
you just got out of Rikers.

632
01:07:41,874 --> 01:07:44,468
Is that true?

633
01:07:44,577 --> 01:07:45,677
What's this about?

634
01:07:45,678 --> 01:07:47,446
Were you home all evening?

635
01:07:47,447 --> 01:07:48,847
No, I was with a friend.

636
01:07:48,848 --> 01:07:52,573
I may be back
with more questions.

637
01:08:01,527 --> 01:08:04,325
No, no.

638
01:08:08,935 --> 01:08:11,927
You didn't see anything?

639
01:08:27,320 --> 01:08:31,790
Rick, you want to give me
a hand with this?

640
01:08:31,791 --> 01:08:33,258
Yo, Bobby!

641
01:08:36,729 --> 01:08:38,263
You're an hour late.

642
01:08:38,264 --> 01:08:41,233
Sorry, man, there's something
going on in my building today.

643
01:08:41,234 --> 01:08:43,004
We need to talk.

644
01:08:44,604 --> 01:08:47,405
You come by the shop
last night?

645
01:08:47,406 --> 01:08:49,033
No.

646
01:08:49,142 --> 01:08:50,242
You sure you didn't come by...

647
01:08:50,243 --> 01:08:51,343
...the shop
last night after closing?

648
01:08:51,344 --> 01:08:52,606
Yeah.

649
01:08:52,712 --> 01:08:54,546
There was a 300 that came in
for a tire balance.

650
01:08:54,547 --> 01:08:56,267
You remember it?

651
01:08:56,315 --> 01:08:57,415
It wasn't mine.

652
01:08:57,416 --> 01:08:59,417
I didn't do a balance yesterday.

653
01:08:59,418 --> 01:09:00,783
It's gone.

654
01:09:00,887 --> 01:09:02,487
I came in this morning,
it was off the lot.

655
01:09:02,488 --> 01:09:07,225
I called up the owner,
she hasn't picked it up yet.

656
01:09:07,226 --> 01:09:11,811
You got something you want
to ask me, man?

657
01:09:12,064 --> 01:09:14,933
Look, my other guys have been
with me for years, Bobby.

658
01:09:14,934 --> 01:09:16,368
All I got on you
is your history.

659
01:09:16,369 --> 01:09:19,804
But I have a situation
with no other answer.

660
01:09:19,805 --> 01:09:21,373
If that 300 gets returned
in the next hour...,

661
01:09:21,374 --> 01:09:22,474
I won't call the cops.

662
01:09:22,475 --> 01:09:23,575
I don't have the car, man.

663
01:09:23,576 --> 01:09:25,777
No, I'm trying to give you
the benefit of the doubt here.

664
01:09:25,778 --> 01:09:27,871
Call the cops, man.

665
01:09:27,980 --> 01:09:29,281
I don't have the car.

666
01:09:29,282 --> 01:09:32,684
I can't keep you on until
that 300 turns up.

667
01:09:32,685 --> 01:09:33,709
Yeah.

668
01:09:33,819 --> 01:09:36,811
All right.

669
01:10:11,591 --> 01:10:14,583
Hello?

670
01:10:17,029 --> 01:10:18,621
Hello?

671
01:10:59,171 --> 01:11:01,105
Yo, what's this?

672
01:11:01,207 --> 01:11:03,141
How the hell did this happen?

673
01:11:03,142 --> 01:11:04,871
Damn, man!

674
01:11:04,977 --> 01:11:06,602
Watch the shop.

675
01:12:23,322 --> 01:12:25,153
Are you okay?

676
01:12:41,040 --> 01:12:43,041
Alyssa Foldes?
Alyssa Foldes.

677
01:12:43,042 --> 01:12:44,441
Anybody...

678
01:12:44,543 --> 01:12:49,674
...nobody knows her?

679
01:12:49,782 --> 01:12:51,015
Alyssa Foldes?

680
01:12:51,016 --> 01:12:53,075
You know Alyssa?

681
01:12:53,185 --> 01:12:55,687
It's really important
that I talk to her.

682
01:12:55,688 --> 01:12:57,212
Sorry.

683
01:12:57,323 --> 01:13:00,058
I don't know where she is.

684
01:13:00,059 --> 01:13:01,253
Come on.

685
01:13:01,360 --> 01:13:03,895
You got to help me out.

686
01:13:06,365 --> 01:13:07,966
She put a lot of trust in you.

687
01:13:07,967 --> 01:13:10,402
And you're going to end up
hurting her again.

688
01:13:10,403 --> 01:13:12,203
She can't deal with that
in her life right now.

689
01:13:12,204 --> 01:13:13,471
You don't know
what's going on.

690
01:13:13,472 --> 01:13:15,006
I know Alyssa
never showed up tonight.

691
01:13:15,007 --> 01:13:16,107
I know she didn't turn in
her final.

692
01:13:16,108 --> 01:13:17,275
And I know she's only been
acting like this...

693
01:13:17,276 --> 01:13:18,376
...since you showed up.

694
01:13:18,377 --> 01:13:20,811
Just leave her alone.

695
01:13:20,913 --> 01:13:23,148
She knows about the other girl.

696
01:13:23,149 --> 01:13:25,379
What other girl?

697
01:13:25,484 --> 01:13:28,444
The woman at your apartment.

698
01:13:28,687 --> 01:13:29,954
Did...did Alyssa talk to her?

699
01:13:29,955 --> 01:13:31,855
Don't know.

700
01:13:31,957 --> 01:13:34,347
Just have her call me.

701
01:13:40,833 --> 01:13:43,097
Bobby, you there?

702
01:13:43,202 --> 01:13:45,864
It's Hector.

703
01:13:45,971 --> 01:13:47,939
The city towed
the wrong car, man.

704
01:13:47,940 --> 01:13:50,275
I'm sorry I doubted you.

705
01:13:50,276 --> 01:13:54,679
You still have your job
if you want it, man.

706
01:13:54,680 --> 01:13:57,672
Bobby!

707
01:14:32,718 --> 01:14:35,203
Are you all right, kid?

708
01:14:55,274 --> 01:14:57,242
Hello?

709
01:14:57,343 --> 01:14:59,573
Little girl?

710
01:14:59,678 --> 01:15:03,079
You all right?

711
01:15:04,817 --> 01:15:08,048
Hello?

712
01:15:08,153 --> 01:15:09,683
Where are you?

713
01:15:14,560 --> 01:15:18,121
Hello?

714
01:15:18,230 --> 01:15:21,222
Little girl?

715
01:16:04,410 --> 01:16:06,037
Help!

716
01:16:06,145 --> 01:16:07,635
Help!

717
01:16:07,746 --> 01:16:08,746
Anybody?

718
01:16:08,847 --> 01:16:14,217
Help!

719
01:16:17,656 --> 01:16:20,648
Damn it!

720
01:16:54,760 --> 01:16:55,954
Hello?

721
01:16:56,061 --> 01:16:57,795
Mr. Reynolds, do you know
what day it is today?

722
01:16:57,796 --> 01:16:58,896
No.
What?

723
01:16:58,897 --> 01:17:01,717
It's your weekly check-in.

724
01:17:02,434 --> 01:17:04,669
Appointments with your PO
are not optional.

725
01:17:04,670 --> 01:17:06,437
I thought we understood
each other.

726
01:17:06,438 --> 01:17:07,438
Yeah.

727
01:17:07,539 --> 01:17:08,631
Sorry.

728
01:17:08,741 --> 01:17:12,321
Is there something
I should know?

729
01:17:15,414 --> 01:17:16,681
Mr. Reynolds?

730
01:17:16,682 --> 01:17:18,449
I can't talk right now.

731
01:17:18,450 --> 01:17:20,551
Look, let me give this to you
in vivid detail.

732
01:17:20,552 --> 01:17:22,754
You speed your way...

733
01:17:22,755 --> 01:17:24,155
...into the parole office
right now...

734
01:17:24,156 --> 01:17:26,858
...or you illegally violate,
and we come looking for you.

735
01:17:26,859 --> 01:17:28,622
You get me?

736
01:17:32,398 --> 01:17:33,783
Mr. Reynolds?

737
01:18:15,340 --> 01:18:17,808
Help...help me!

738
01:18:17,910 --> 01:18:19,911
I know you're in there!
Please!

739
01:18:19,912 --> 01:18:22,574
Please open the door!

740
01:19:09,261 --> 01:19:10,261
Bobby?

741
01:19:10,362 --> 01:19:12,853
Bobby, can you hear me?

742
01:19:12,965 --> 01:19:14,198
Look, um, those...

743
01:19:14,199 --> 01:19:16,234
...those noises that you heard,
I think...

744
01:19:16,235 --> 01:19:17,568
...I think I may be
hearing them too.

745
01:19:17,569 --> 01:19:19,103
I don't understand
what's happening.

746
01:19:19,104 --> 01:19:20,838
You were trying to tell me
something...

747
01:19:20,839 --> 01:19:22,306
...and I didn't listen,
and I'm sorry.

748
01:19:22,307 --> 01:19:26,847
And I'm going to come
and find you, okay?

749
01:19:48,400 --> 01:19:49,930
Open the door!

750
01:20:00,179 --> 01:20:01,179
Bobby?

751
01:20:21,567 --> 01:20:24,836
Think I don't know
you're in there?

752
01:20:24,837 --> 01:20:27,362
I don't want trouble.

753
01:20:27,472 --> 01:20:29,407
You've been watching me.
I see you in the window.

754
01:20:29,408 --> 01:20:31,988
What are you looking at?

755
01:20:32,177 --> 01:20:35,707
Something happened
on that floor.

756
01:20:40,786 --> 01:20:42,854
You know something, don't you?

757
01:20:42,855 --> 01:20:46,357
There was this family
living there.

758
01:20:46,358 --> 01:20:48,826
One night...,

759
01:20:48,927 --> 01:20:50,595
...the mother, she kept screaming.

760
01:20:50,596 --> 01:20:52,587
No.

761
01:20:52,698 --> 01:20:55,861
Don't!

762
01:20:55,968 --> 01:20:58,562
But nobody helped her.

763
01:21:00,505 --> 01:21:01,772
It doesn't make sense.

764
01:21:01,773 --> 01:21:03,674
You could...you could have
just called the cops.

765
01:21:03,675 --> 01:21:05,977
A lot of terrible things
happen in this city every day.

766
01:21:05,978 --> 01:21:09,280
Either we assumed someone
would call the police...,

767
01:21:09,281 --> 01:21:13,006
...or we were afraid to,
or worse.

768
01:21:13,819 --> 01:21:17,448
Some of us just didn't care.

769
01:21:17,556 --> 01:21:21,566
The next morning,
they were all dead.

770
01:21:29,801 --> 01:21:32,793
It's your fault.

771
01:21:36,875 --> 01:21:39,043
You could have done something.

772
01:21:39,044 --> 01:21:40,144
You let them die.

773
01:21:40,145 --> 01:21:42,313
Any one of you,
my mother included...,

774
01:21:42,314 --> 01:21:43,414
...could have saved them.

775
01:21:43,415 --> 01:21:45,781
You realize that?

776
01:21:52,591 --> 01:21:54,836
Hey, hey, hey!
Wait!

777
01:21:54,900 --> 01:21:56,728
I'm sorry! I can't help you!

778
01:21:56,729 --> 01:21:59,549
Why...why won't they stop?

779
01:22:06,972 --> 01:22:10,203
Hello, Miss?

780
01:22:10,309 --> 01:22:11,409
Is he in there?

781
01:22:11,410 --> 01:22:14,230
I really need to find him.

782
01:22:24,623 --> 01:22:28,286
Anyone home?

783
01:22:34,299 --> 01:22:38,633
Sorry, I...

784
01:22:38,737 --> 01:22:43,272
...the woman who walked
in here, do you...

785
01:24:55,107 --> 01:24:56,240
Oh, my God!

786
01:24:56,241 --> 01:24:57,241
Alyssa?

787
01:24:57,342 --> 01:24:59,674
Alyssa!

788
01:24:59,778 --> 01:25:00,911
I'm so sorry.

789
01:25:00,912 --> 01:25:02,937
I'm so sorry.

790
01:25:03,048 --> 01:25:04,709
Oh, my God.

791
01:25:04,816 --> 01:25:07,446
What did they do to you?

792
01:25:11,456 --> 01:25:12,980
Oh, God.

793
01:25:13,091 --> 01:25:15,082
Oh, God.

794
01:25:15,193 --> 01:25:16,193
Please.

795
01:25:16,294 --> 01:25:18,295
911...
What is your emergency?

796
01:25:18,296 --> 01:25:19,897
I...I need an ambulance.

797
01:25:19,898 --> 01:25:21,866
Please.

798
01:25:21,967 --> 01:25:25,117
What is your current location?

799
01:25:27,272 --> 01:25:28,864
Sir?

800
01:25:28,974 --> 01:25:30,744
Can you hear me?

801
01:25:31,977 --> 01:25:32,977
Sir?

802
01:25:34,412 --> 01:25:36,413
You're doing real good, honey.

803
01:25:36,414 --> 01:25:38,415
Everything's going to be okay.

804
01:25:38,416 --> 01:25:42,219
But I want you to be strong
for mommy.

805
01:25:42,220 --> 01:25:43,983
You got me?

806
01:25:44,089 --> 01:25:45,756
Right.
Let me see that pretty smile.

807
01:25:45,757 --> 01:25:48,749
There.

808
01:25:57,936 --> 01:26:00,516
Hey, what are you doing?

809
01:26:02,374 --> 01:26:06,572
Please don't do this.

810
01:26:06,678 --> 01:26:11,581
Don't do what?

811
01:26:18,290 --> 01:26:19,820
We're leaving.

812
01:26:24,362 --> 01:26:26,512
Why are you leaving?

813
01:26:28,066 --> 01:26:29,166
You know why.

814
01:26:29,167 --> 01:26:30,267
- But you...
- Don't!

815
01:26:30,268 --> 01:26:32,069
You can't leave.
Whoa, whoa.

816
01:26:32,070 --> 01:26:34,030
What?
Don't what?

817
01:26:35,440 --> 01:26:36,774
Shh, it's okay.

818
01:26:36,775 --> 01:26:40,176
It's okay.

819
01:26:40,278 --> 01:26:41,808
Where are you?

820
01:26:41,880 --> 01:26:46,977
Here, here, here,
here, here, here.

821
01:26:48,186 --> 01:26:49,761
Listen, listen.

822
01:26:51,122 --> 01:26:52,756
You just close your eyes...

823
01:26:52,757 --> 01:26:55,626
...and go to that special place
like always.

824
01:26:55,627 --> 01:26:57,094
Nothing else will matter.

825
01:26:57,095 --> 01:26:58,195
Carly, are you okay?

826
01:26:58,196 --> 01:26:59,363
Why are you crying?
What...

827
01:26:59,364 --> 01:27:00,695
No.

828
01:27:00,799 --> 01:27:03,968
I...I really don't understand
what's happening here.

829
01:27:03,969 --> 01:27:05,449
What...what...

